. Slowly dilute the virus to the tube volume with 50 mM Tris-HCl. Centrifuge the tubes in the ultracentrifuge\u00a0at 27,000 rpm, 3 hours, 4\u00baC. Discard the supernatants.<\/p>","order_id":"1","name":"Description","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"1","source_data":{"description":"<p>Remove the virus bands from the gradients with sterile needles and transfer to 30 mL polypropylene centrifuge tubes. Split the virus from 3 gradients between two tubes. Slowly dilute the virus to the tube volume with 50 mM Tris-HCl. Centrifuge the tubes in the ultracentrifuge\u00a0at 27,000 rpm, 3 hours, 4\u00baC. Discard the supernatants.<\/p>"},"is_project":0}]},{"id":"300210","is_changed":"0","original_id":"0","is_skipped":"0","is_checked":"0","guid":"543F16CC20F34CC8BEF3197E229825EB","previous_guid":"4A264E92EEAA4498802C531C254F2978","previous_id":"300209","last_modified":"1502719046","components":[{"component_id":"990142","previous_id":0,"original_id":"0","guid":"7A0AC96892EB4CF3AD2750E683C75DE8","previous_guid":null,"component_type_id":"6","data_id":null,"data":null,"order_id":"0","name":"Section","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"6","source_data":{"section":null},"is_project":0},{"component_id":"438073","previous_id":"990142","original_id":"0","guid":"627EFECB8EC447029A076167E371BFF5","previous_guid":"7A0AC96892EB4CF3AD2750E683C75DE8","component_type_id":"1","data_id":"0","data":"<p>Resuspend the virus pellets with a small volume of 50 mM Tris-HCl. Store the virus at 4\u00baC. Do not freeze. Filter sterilization using a 0.45 um cellulose acetate filter is recommended.<\/p>","order_id":"1","name":"Description","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"1","source_data":{"description":"<p>Resuspend the virus pellets with a small volume of 50 mM Tris-HCl. Store the virus at 4\u00baC. Do not freeze. Filter sterilization using a 0.45 um cellulose acetate filter is recommended.<\/p>"},"is_project":0}]}]}